			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Karen Vogel</span></strong> is not Canadian but moved to Schomberg, Ontario, Canada, for the love of her husband, a Polish-Canadian cellist whom she met in Poland and decided to marry one week later. In her spare time she edits Wikipedia articles and posts to her blog, <em>Dear Mister Baby</em>. &ldquo;The First Year&rdquo; is her first published essay.</p><a href="/contributors/karen-vogel" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
